All Classes

Class
Description
Animal
Class for animal pieces to be used in the GameBoard class.
GameBoard
Stores the main game board composed of Tile objects and controls movement of pieces within the board.
Player
The Player object lists down all animal pieces held by a player, both owned and captured pieces.
Position
An object denoting the location of another object in the GameBoard.
Terrain
Enumeration to classify specific colors of dens and special terrain in the Tile class.
TestMain
Test driver for testing the implementation of Classes in the src package.
Tile
Represents a location for Animal objects and special Terrain enumerations.
